These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, thai
1. the polish is on the left or right of the thai##3
2. the thai is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Nationality   | polish | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
