1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Sport   | climbing | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Pet   | rabbit | hedgehog |

